In case anyone is having issues with Boilerkey, here is how it works after you’ve set it up:

Type “<your 4 digit pin>,push” in the password feild while logging into myPurdue, Blackboards, etc. It’ll send a notification to the duo app on your phone. Approve that request within 15 seconds and it’ll automatically log you in. You can approve the notification request on iPhones using 3D Touch instead of having to open the app.

“<4 digit pin>,<code in duo app>” should work too. I believe, the code can’t be more than 15 seconds old though so refresh it before typing it. This second method will let you login without approving a notification but you’ll have to open the app.
